To enable [[Elastic audio]] go to '''Pro Tools/Preferences/Processing''' and then check the box that says '''Enable elastic audio on new tracks.'''



Then to enable elastic audio on an individual track click the elastic audio icon on the track header


[[File:Pro Tools Elastic audio track icon .png]]




[[File:Pro Tools elastic audio track header menu .png]]


If you select a region you can then manipulate the elastic audio properties for it by going to '''Region/Elastic properties''' 

[[File:Pro Tools Elastic audio menu.png]]






[[File:Pro Tools elastic properties parameters .png]]


